results.title: A mysterious myopic surprise.
results.text_hl: His past medical history is significant for @DISEASE_Hypertension @DISEASE_MESH:D006973 @@@hypertension@@@ and @<m>DISEASE_Prostatic_Hyperplasia</m> @DISEASE_MESH:D011470 @@@benign prostatic hyperplasia@@@, and his oral medications include @CHEMICAL_Tamsulosin @CHEMICAL_MESH:D000077409 @@@Tamsulosin@@@ (@CHEMICAL_Tamsulosin @CHEMICAL_MESH:D000077409 @@@Flomax@@@), Irbasartan (@CHEMICAL_Irbesartan @CHEMICAL_MESH:D000077405 @@@Avapro@@@), and @<m>CHEMICAL_Atenolol</m> @CHEMICAL_MESH:D001262 @@@Atenolol@@@.
